エリカ DS_ST05-1
\n< Erika >Serena! It's dangerous!

\n< Serena >I apologize. But I'll be fine. Arrows of that
level won't penetrate my armor!

\n< Erika >There must be limits! Tch, they've got the
entrance covered. I can't recklessly go out,
that's for sure.

\n< Serena >...Are they planning to attack us after not
letting us escape and waiting for reinforcements?
If that's the case, we don't have much time. I
will find a way out here...

\n< Erika >...No, I told you I have a plan, Serena. Let's
quickly go to the storage area for the loot.
\n< Serena >......Hmm.

\n< Erika >I'm going to shoot you again, Serena. The loot
storage is upstairs.
\n< Serena >Alright, we've reached the exit.

\n< Serena >We've managed to handle things well so far, but
there should still be a few thieves remaining
outside.
\n< Serena >We'll have to fight those guys. Are you ready?

\n< Erika >There's no good or bad. If we stay here any
longer, we'll end up dead. It's a gamble once
we're out.
\n< Serena >Alright, let's go!

\n< Erika >Serena, please wait a moment.

\n< Serena >What's wrong, Erika? We need to escape quickly or
we'll be engulfed in flames too.

\n< Erika >What's wrong? It'll be done in no time... I'm just
finishing up, ya know!!

\n< Erika >The only escape route left is a sea of fire. We
either burn to death or jump off, a delightful
choice, you bastards!

\n< Serena >...With this, it seems like we can avoid any
possible pursuit. Well done, Erika-sama.
\n< Erika >Hehe, it's not that big of a deal. Now, let's go.
